Package: libcdk-pixbuf-2.0-0
Architecture: any
Depends: libcdk-pixbuf2.0-common (>= ${source:Version}),
         shared-mime-info,
         ${misc:Depends},
         ${shlibs:Depends}
Recommends: libcdk-pixbuf2.0-bin
Multi-Arch: same
Description: CDK Pixbuf library
 The CDK Pixbuf library provides:
  - Image loading and saving facilities.
  - Fast scaling and compositing of pixbufs.
  - Simple animation loading (ie. animated GIFs)

Package: libcdk-pixbuf2.0-bin
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}
Multi-Arch: foreign
Description: CDK Pixbuf library (thumbnailer)
 The CDK Pixbuf library provides:
  - Image loading and saving facilities.
  - Fast scaling and compositing of pixbufs.
  - Simple animation loading (ie. animated GIFs)
 .
 This package contains the CDK pixdata compression utility, the thumbnailer
 and a utility for converting images into C code.

Package: libcdk-pixbuf2.0-common
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Multi-Arch: foreign
Description: CDK Pixbuf library - data files
 This package contains the common files and translations for the CDK
 Pixbuf library.

